Dutch to English translation
directed by D.J. Caruso
Alex Pettyfer, Timothy Olyphant and Dianna Agron

Nine alien babies with human characteristics flee from their home planet Lorien to hide on Earth.
They are followed by the Mogadorians who have destroyed their own planet for the babies to detect.
The babies all have their own bodyguard, and they will get super powers when they get older.
They all have a SSN number to nine and can only be killed in that order. Number Four (Alex Pettyfer)
Smith also named John, moved to Paradise, Ohio and is friends with the friendly photographer Sarah.
After his entire life on the lam, he is Number Four and is in love with Sarah, who is worth fighting for.
